title: Tilly's Shopping Spree with Levi's BMX PRO Anthony Napolitan
description: Video footage from the Red Bull BMX Demo with Levi's BMX Pros, Anthony Napolitan and Corey Martinez, at Brian Piccolo Skate / BMX Park in Pembroke Pines, Florida on December 13th, 2010. At the demo two lucky winners received a $250 after-hours shopping spree at Tilly's in Pembroke Lakes Mall!
